Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OMNI-AGENT. Your Marines have 53 AI tools - this is the one that picks\Nthe right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross-domain decisions: blood readiness is a weather problem is a\Nsustainment problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourteen sibling apps wired as governed tools - the Kamiwaza Tool\NGarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,VITALS, WEATHERVANE, MERIDIAN, CONTESTED-LOG, REORDER, CUAS-DETECT,\NOMNI...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One operator query. The agent decomposes and fires three tools in\Nsequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,VITALS reports blood readiness. WEATHERVANE confirms the typhoon\Nwindow. MERIDIAN scores nodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed model fuses every result into one OPORD-style\Nbrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every tool invocation is SHA-256 hash-chain audited for SJA forensics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL - the orchestration layer stays inside your\Nenclave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OMNI-AGENT - Kamiwaza unifies your AI fleet. Powered by the Kamiwaza\NStack.
